{"tid":605080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波派錢都蠢過人","createTime":"2018-03-25T10:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T18:05:48.000Z","uid":32723,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0eb5849a8fb60dbe038603da8ea2116858f10f26","tid":605080,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T10:32:58.000Z","msg":"全民派四千咪攪掂 洗鬼攪咁多野<br />\n<br />\n行爾費仲貴過派錢"},{"pid":"8a3543288a09d745d325761bb08987bfd9420e9c","tid":605080,"uid":16676,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T10:36:22.000Z","msg":"呢個垃圾正苦, 識改變<span style=\"color: red;\">企業利得稅成兩級制</span><br />\n但又無趁機會同企業傾條件 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大把稅收, 盈餘下, <br />\n只要撥多d 錢落去MPF 對衝果度, 好快就成事<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">垃圾預算案, 搵個無能兼無腦會計佬去做財爺起劏房波</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">反而MPF 對衝<br />\n全民退保, 醫保<br />\n勞工假<br />\n立法5天工作制<br />\n最高工時<br />\n</span><br />\n呢d 實事, 隨時仲簡單又唔去做, 推都唔撚識推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2蚊乘車, 以前殖民地推既話, 點會由正苦比架<br />\n一定由港督由商界(太古 etc ) 帶頭自己做, <br />\n國泰工會點解咁強大, 都係當年前港英正苦要太古放權<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳門已立法規定<br />\n強制性假日返工要比三糧「三工」<br />\n<br />\n香港法例仍然係講緊最少要比員工放勞工假咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n帶頭無條件減利得稅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7056a2325763505ca074d5ab143ed32a8068989f","tid":605080,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T11:01:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26ba437ba1ea0191e768d38f28ec7a43c6dc6a23","tid":605080,"uid":52960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T11:29:53.000Z","msg":"立法5天工作, 最高時,<br />\n即是要僱主請更多人?<br /